<plot>The films follow Anthropologist Dr. Luisa Elvira as she investigates the little-known, exotic and dramatic indigenous sports of Latin America. Travelling from rural Mexico to the Peruvian Andes, and from the Brazilian Mato Grosso to the shanty towns of Bahia, the films explore the richness of ancient Latin American culture and traditions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?009649</url></doc>
